OL,3,CCase of killer nurse Beverley Allitt
OL,4,Cwas part of Lucy Letby's training -
OL,5,Cinquiry
OL,7,FThe case of serial killer Beverley
OL,8,FAllitt formed part of nurse Lucy
OL,9,FLetby's training, a public inquiry has
OL,10,Fheard.
OL,12,FThe Thirlwall Inquiry, which will
OL,13,Fprobe how Letby was able to attack
OL,14,Fbabies on the Countess of Chester
OL,15,FHospital's neo-natal unit in 2015 and
OL,16,F2016, opened on Tuesday with a
OL,17,Fstatement which referenced nurse
OL,18,FAllitt, who attacked children at the
OL,19,FGrantham and Kesteven Hospital,
OL,20,FLincolnshire, in 1991, and killer GP
OL,21,FHarold Shipman.
