OL,5,Cinquiry
OL,7,FChairwoman Lady Justice Thirlwall said
OL,8,Fthe inquiry would not examine Letby's
OL,9,Fconvictions, saying an "outpouring of
OL,10,Fcomment" on their validity had "caused
OL,11,Fenormous additional distress to the
OL,12,Fparents".
OL,14,FThe 34-year-old, from Hereford, is
OL,15,Fserving 15 whole-life orders after she
OL,16,Fwas convicted at Manchester Crown
OL,17,FCourt of murdering seven infants and
OL,18,Fattempting to murder seven others,
OL,19,Fwith two attempts on one of her
OL,20,Fvictims.
