OL,5,Cinquiry
OL,7,FIn her opening statement at Liverpool
OL,8,FTown Hall, counsel to the inquiry
OL,9,FRachel Langdale KC said the Clothier
OL,10,FInquiry had been carried out following
OL,11,Fthe crimes of Allitt, who was
OL,12,Fconvicted of four counts of murder,
OL,13,Fthree of attempted murder, and a
OL,14,Ffurther six of grievous bodily harm on
OL,15,Fchildren.
OL,17,FShe said: "Nevertheless, and
OL,18,Fdistressingly, 25 years later another
OL,19,Fnurse working in another hospital
OL,20,Fkilled and harmed babies in her care."
