OL,7,FMs Langdale said the inquiry would
OL,8,Fhear from a senior lecturer in the
OL,9,Fchild nursing programme at the
OL,10,FUniversity of Chester, where Letby
OL,11,Fqualified in 2011, who said the case
OL,12,Fof Allitt formed part of student
OL,13,Ftraining and learning.
