OL,3,CCase of killer nurse Beverley Allitt
OL,4,Cwas part of Lucy Letby's training -
OL,5,Cinquiry
OL,7,FShe said the motive for Letby's crimes
OL,8,Fwould not be examined during the
OL,9,Fhearings, and referenced an inquiry
OL,10,Finto the crimes of Shipman, thought to
OL,11,Fhave murdered hundreds of his
OL,12,Fpatients, which "shed very little
OL,13,Flight" on why he carried out the
OL,14,Fkillings.
OL,16,FShe said: "For ordinary, decent, right-
OL,17,Fthinking people, the actions of Letby
OL,18,Fwill remain unfathomable. We will not
OL,19,Fbe inviting speculation from witnesses
OL,20,Fabout her motive or mindset."
